{"tid":1699703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎睇下韓國罷工點先成功!!","createTime":"2019-11-08T06:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T13:10:04.000Z","uid":105976,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"602be2a10050c37318c90f4e889a1e9653ff5ac1","tid":1699703,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:35:46.000Z","msg":"韓國1996-7 工人大罷工 <br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1996%E2%80%9397_strikes_in_South_Korea\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F1996%25E2%2580%259397_strikes_in_South_Korea&d=6wykgBqlsxypO2QI0oCEUgogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=ed6b0c25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/1996%E2%80%9397_strikes_in_South_Korea</a><br />\n<br />\n過程:  <br />\nDec 26  120萬工人大罷工  <br />\nDec27    罷工擴展至其他行業<br />\n<br />\n January 6,  工會領袖號召14號再開始大罷工 ,  南韓政府恐嚇扣捕 <br />\n<br />\nJan  14, 工會宣佈1月14日罷工非常成功  120萬成員中有70萬響應罷工<br />\n學生農民全力支持  民意有7成支持<br />\n得到國際性勞工組織 例如AFL-CIO 支持<br />\n得到國際政府支持 (如澳洲)<br />\n<br />\nJanuary 16,  防暴警濫暴 放TG<br />\n<br />\nJanuary 18   工會指每星期3 都罷工  直至2月18 ,每周末大遊行<br />\n, 然後回復無限期罷工 ,<br />\n<br />\nJanuary 20,  總統和工會領袖會面  <br />\n<br />\nJanuary 24 第2大鋼業公司破產  ,  令更多政府醜聞暴光<br />\n另一方面勞工因經濟壓力不太願意繼續大罷工<br />\n<br />\n結果:<br />\nMarch10, 雖然法案最後沒有大更動, 但延遲了2年才實行, 而且相關勞工福利仍然在世上數一數二,  該運動算是韓國<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成功: 有工會     行業入面有一半人罷工就已經成功令佢停擺<br />\n有國際支持  有民意支持<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反思: 過完年之後 大罷工左2日之後變左每星期罷一次,  拖左個幾月之後工人們有經濟壓力唔可以重返大罷工,  所以要罷就一口氣罷  , <br />\n<br />\n有國際支持好重要, 要打國際戰線等大公司唔敢清算<br />\n<br />\n清算員工既公司會被香港人/國際清算返</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0b3e64fa8276d1b687b1b2fbdfab42b270b1b5d6","tid":1699703,"uid":273723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:39:05.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n我宣布三罷籌備工作正式開始<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1688552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1688552</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e27edebee7abafc3a7f1c2431ce8a2ec757dd7f6","tid":1699703,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:39:38.000Z","msg":"該運動算是韓國戰後成功的罷工運動  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07b4ad62b0d1e3d3c8310d3bff8ef7ff85cdefb","tid":1699703,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:45:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c51d2074f539eab00e9277555a38fd372ea835c","tid":1699703,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"213dac858607ed0a0bd8b6d6e0064a829450df3f","tid":1699703,"uid":29625,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:51:54.000Z","msg":"個重點係工會<br />\n無工會嘅所謂罷工注定響應人數少+唔會持久<br />\n呢個係無法撼動嘅事實<br />\n明明過去幾日都討論咗好多 亦都有手足不斷呼籲人一齊著手籌備<br />\n但係今日新聞一出就拋諸腦後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99319b6a81105d1f9d1e63037f443803dd4da124","tid":1699703,"uid":286771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"213dac858607ed0a0bd8b6d6e0064a829450df3f","tid":1699703,"uid":29625,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T06:51:54.000Z","msg":"個重點係工會<br />\n無工會嘅所謂罷工注定響應人數少+唔會持久<br />\n呢個係無法撼動嘅事實<br />\n明明過去幾日都討論咗好多 亦都有手足不斷呼籲人一齊著手籌備<br />\n但係今日新聞一出就拋諸腦後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"我諗係咪仲籌備緊?<br />\n想再叫多d人黎<br />\n今日新聞出左一定會暫時轉移左視線<br />\n但大家如果想對得住周同學嘅話一定會加緊腳步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc91b6e33b2e1859d5b95b4cf077331505f4d0b","tid":1699703,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T07:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1110cdd9e5f8237365940a9002155f73f7a498d7","tid":1699703,"uid":1059